        <div class="row">
            <div class="mb-3" name="statement_container">
                <label>
                    <input
                        type="checkbox"
                        t-att-value="statement"
                        name="statement"
                        required="True"
                    />
                    Titularity statement
                </label>
                <p>I hereby declare that I (or the entity I represent) have a valid title to the home or premises (lease agreement, property deed, or other) related to the reference supply point and/or CUPS of which I am a valid user, assuming full responsibility for the accuracy of the information provided. I also declare that I am able to provide documentation proving said valid title when requested.</p>
